# FinTrack AI — Core Context

**App:** Personal finance web app for Vietnamese millennials. Features: AI-assisted transaction recording (Vietnamese NLP), budget tracking with color alerts, investment portfolio, financial reports.

**Full docs:** Always read the relevant file before modifying a domain.
- `docs/ai/architecture.md` — system architecture, domain modules, data flows
- `docs/ai/data-model.md` — all 9 DB tables with column types and relationships
- `docs/ai/conventions.md` — naming conventions, coding patterns, anti-patterns
- `docs/ai/known-issues.md` — active bugs with root causes and exact fixes

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 19, TypeScript 5.9, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui |
| API | tRPC 11 (no REST endpoints) |
| ORM / DB | Drizzle ORM 0.44 + PostgreSQL (Supabase) |
| Auth | JWT session cookie — `protectedProcedure` in every protected route |
| AI/LLM | OpenAI-compatible API via `ENV.forgeApiKey` / `ENV.forgeApiUrl` |
| Routing | wouter 3 |
| Charts | Recharts 2 |
| Icons | lucide-react |

## Domain Map

| Domain | Router prefix | Page file |
|---|---|---|
| Auth | `auth.*` | — (DashboardLayout guard) |
| Category + Budget | `category.*` | `Categories.tsx` |
