| Dashboard | (aggregates above) | `Dashboard.tsx` |

## Environment Variables

```typescript
// Server side — use ENV from server/_core/env.ts
ENV.forgeApiKey   // LLM API key
ENV.forgeApiUrl   // LLM API URL
ENV.jwtSecret     // Session signing
ENV.ownerOpenId   // Admin/seed subject id

// Client side — Vite
import.meta.env.VITE_*
```

Never hardcode secrets. Never import ENV on the client.
